sub_title: 🌱 Making mental well-being accessible to all at OpenUp | Empowering companies to take care of their most valuable assets: their employees
summary:
Hi there! 

A little something about me;
I'm an experienced and strategic Account Manager/Executive with a demonstrated and successful track record (mostly in the tech industry), managing the implementation of SaaS, data & insights, talent and advertising solutions for global companies. Skilled in Relationship Management, New Business Development, Negotiation, Sales Operations, Ad campaigns and Media Sales, Employer Branding and Recruiting. 

From my experience I can demonstrate a history of working in both B2B as B2C. 
Due to my international travels through >60 countries, I am able to keep things in perspective, adapt easily to various situations and people and have a very optimistic, adventurous and open approach to life.

I would describe myself as straight to the point but warm and honest, responsible, highly social and energetic, pragmatic and executive. Next to that; FUN is one of my core values, as I’m always enjoying life as much as possible and I truly believe that I’m the best version of myself when I’m also striving this in my work!

Currently I'm super proud to work for a company as OpenUp where I can really make an impact, with our mission to make mental well-being accessible to all. 
I'm supporting this by empowering Large Enterprise companies in the Netherlands to take care of their most valuable assets: their employees. 

I truly believe mental wellbeing at work is essential for success and this really is the perfect time to OpenUp. 

Feel free to reach out to me if you would like to learn more on how we can help your company with their well-being.

Email: jessicablanckaert@openup.com
Phone: +3147350411
Website: www.openup.com

profile_positions.description:
OpenUp is an innovative, online platform focused on mental health with a mission to make mental well-being accessible to all. Easy, affordable, and direct.

We do this by offering businesses and individuals unlimited and anonymous , fast, and secure access to consultations with licensed psychologists within 24 hours and in 25+ languages.

In addition, we promote the discussion of mental well-being through various formats:

- Mindfulness sessions (alone or in groups)
- Group sessions to tackle challenges together
- Masterclasses to learn more about mental health
- Blogposts to learn more about current topics

Not only when life challenges us, but also before: in a preventive manner. 
Because in the end, it’s all about supporting people. 

💡 In numbers: OpenUp works with over 1100+ companies in Europe, helping to improve the mental well-being of over 200.000 employees. 

Want to know more? 
Find out how OpenUp can support your organisation and send me a message:

✉ Email: jessicablanckaert@openup.com
Website: www.openup.com
